## v4.0.0

- Complete rewrite of the project
- Upgraded image handling to use Fresco
- Replaced promises with RxAndroid
- Upgraded user profiles
- Improved efficiency and multi-threading
- Brought architecture up to date with iOS
- Made the project more modular
- Upgraded all project dependencies

## v4.0.7

- Multiple bug fixes
- Removed PagerSlidingTabBar in favor of native TabLayout 